39:23.762 --> 39:24.898
- You had everyone
up in arms today.

39:25.465 --> 39:26.932
- About what? What'd I do?

39:27.329 --> 39:30.536
- You made a little comment
that went everywhere.

39:30.570 --> 39:31.938
- Oh (BLEEP).

