- You said that we're
all coming after you.

39:33.672 --> 39:34.641
- What? What? What?

39:34.673 --> 39:36.443
<i>- She did some
interview on "Ellen" today</i>

39:36.476 --> 39:37.476
<i>with Mario Lopez</i>

