down watching this all go down.

42:10.563 --> 42:13.132
- I think you may have to go
over there and chop some heads.

42:13.166 --> 42:15.135
- Not yet, do you
think? Not yet.

42:15.168 --> 42:19.739
<i>Garcelle got called out
for being jabby and shady.</i>

42:19.773 --> 42:23.610
If I feel there's
injustice going on,

42:23.643 --> 42:26.545
